{"tid":783663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理大鐘劍華收到第二封律師信   鐘劍華：可以用蠻不講理，發爛渣來形容","createTime":"2018-08-17T16:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T00:16:19.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"57d0d2035b23ff2f61debdc15902e36ace691ad6","tid":783663,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:46:56.000Z","msg":"今日收到第二封律師信<br />\n<br />\n可以用蠻不講理，發爛渣來形容。<br />\n小學雞到跌穿了想像力的底線。<br />\n<br />\n今次決定唔再回應佢。<br />\n<br />\n我就當做個campaign，到時最多咪搞眾籌。<br />\n到時就搞個 movement 出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n余若薇大狀在其節目中話 「CY 律師信苦主大聯盟」又多咗個人。<br />\n我不同意這個說法。<br />\n<br />\n真正的「苦主」是那種無法面對事實，無法透過講出套道理來證明自己的可憐蟲！<br />\n<br />\n我不會做鶕鶉的。各位朋友放心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/543236937/posts/10155787711136938/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F543236937%2Fposts%2F10155787711136938%2F&d=ZNJE44%2FX61GjFTrrixCz7BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=6bc8c092\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/543236937/posts/10155787711136938/</a>"},{"pid":"76be127ac52cac7253d26a1b9284dc798de2ca09","tid":783663,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T19:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65005dc223448406e263116c6897c0c0f843803","tid":783663,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T00:16:19.000Z","msg":"每次佢出律師信就證明講中左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}